It makes you so proud to be Canadian. This beer complex aroma reminds me of the oktoberfest latrine in Munich. The low gravity beer allow you to drink a lot before getting drunk, so you can taste this magnificent beer again and again. God bless the Queen, Canada and Stephen Harper
